           模拟演练进行中 <span className="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-indigo-500 animate-ping"></span>
        </div>
        <h2 className="text-6xl font-black tracking-tighter uppercase italic text-white">
          反诈<span className="text-indigo-500">模拟室</span>
